data.description: Income generating legal 3 flat. Zoning has been updated with City of Chicago. First floor is split into (2) units. Second floor is the owner's unit that has undergone full renovation. Ideal for an investor looking to house-hack, live in one unit and rent out the rest to offset mortgage or for a seasoned investor who would like to add to portfolio. Property has room for value add. Rents YoY have steadily continued to increase due to supply and demand making multi family properties more desirable. Seller is open to providing some credit towards rate buy down / seller credit to reduce cash to close
